## **Q82 (Time & Work)**

A can complete a work in **8 days** and B in **12 days**. Working together, they will complete the work in:

A) 4.8 days

B) 5 days

C) 6 days

D) 7 days

✅ **Answer:** **A) 4.8 days**

### **Explanation**

[
\frac{1}{T}=\frac18+\frac1{12}=\frac5{24}
]

[
T=\frac{24}{5}=4.8\text{ days}
]

⭐ **CDS Short Trick**

Together time = **ab/(a+b)**.

