## **Q100 (Geometry)**

The sum of the interior angles of a **50-sided polygon** is:

A) 8460°

B) 8640°

C) 8820°

D) 9000°

✅ **Answer:** **B) 8640°**

### **Explanation**

[
(50-2)\times180
=48\times180
=8640^\circ
]

⭐ **CDS Short Trick**

Interior angle sum = **(n − 2) × 180°**.

